                        <p>For the past two summers, ATP has been promoting a four-day Eco Camp program that has reached thousands of children. The program includes hands-on lessons on river and forest ecosystems, biodiversity, fire prevention, and waste management.</p>
                        <p>Our goal is to create teaching tools and programs that will promote environmental stewardship, connections between youth, problem solving skills, and an opportunity to get outdoors into nature during the long summer months.</p>
